bug.short_desc: show artifact hierarchy in build editor

long_desc.thetext:
The Artifacts section of the build editor currently shows a flattened list of artifacts. This makes them difficult to disambiguate when build generates artifacts with the same name but in different folders (as JGit does).
A folder hierarchy layout would make it easier to navigate for these cases.
Created attachment 200224 Show build artifacts in nested folders
Nice! I have pushed the patch in 3e2527656eb7b6d90d7aa708eff7c3cfab4a1ff1 .
